    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, meticulously maintained and preserved in collector-quality condition. At its heart is the high-revving S54B32 3.2L atmospheric inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that has been professionally overhauled for long-term reliability. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is structurally sound, with proactive subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension geometry utilizing OEM components to maintain its legendary handling characteristics. The exterior retains its original factory finish with zero oxidation, while the cabin features pristine Nappa leather and intact bolster integrity. Complete with a comprehensive service dossier and recent valve adjustment, this is a turn-key example of BMW\u2019s peak engineering era.",
