      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a drop of rain. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any creases, while the original floor mats show no signs of wear. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the touch-screen interface, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is flawless, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by authorized technicians. It features exceptionally low mileage, original alloy wheels with no curb rash, and has never been modified or smoked in. This is a rare opportunity to own a turn-key example that looks and drives as if it just left the dealership. Complete with all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a clean title in hand.",
