      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This car has been pampered since day one\u2014honestly, it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve kept it garage-stored and babied it, so there\u2019s not a single scratch or dent to be found. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for something that's basically brand new without the dealership headache, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
