      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated longitudinal engineering. Featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant, the engine exhibits perfect compression across all six cylinders with the VANOS system recently overhauled for optimal variable valve timing. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp, mechanical engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential that ensures linear power delivery. The chassis is structurally flawless, with the rear subframe mounting points reinforced\u2014a critical preventative measure. Every bushing is tight, and the suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, offering the communicative handling and tactile feedback that defined an era. This is a collector-grade example with zero deferred maintenance.",
